MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

99-869. Tribett v. Mestek, Inc.

Jefferson App. No. 99JE1. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of the applications for dismissal by Mestek, Inc. and Wheeling Pittsburgh Steel Corporation,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the applications for dismissal be, and hereby are, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
